Package se3projecta.Model

This package contains classes that control the functionality of the Application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CustomerType Allows different types of customers to book seats for different prices.
Movie A movie which may be viewable in multiple TheatreSessions.
Seat Allows individual seats to be booked as part of a TheatreSession.
SeatType Allows different types of seats to be booked for different prices.
SessionTime A time for which a theatre can be booked
Theatre Allows description of a Seating Plan for a specific Theatre.
TheatreSession Allows Booking of Seats for a particular SessionTime for a particular Theatre.
 

Enum Summary
SeatState SeatState defines whether a Seat is Empty (not booked or allocated), Held (allocated but not booked), or Occupied (Booked).
 

Exception Summary
ExistingKeyException Exception class for exception thrown when an element is inserted into a collection that already contains the key that is the same as that of the new element.
InvalidRelationException Exception class for exception thrown when a Model class tries to load a non-existent relation
